  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prepare for a chaotic top-down, fast-paced shootout where you, as the Sphere, will fight the straight lines and rigid angles. Start with basic skills and grind your way through hordes of minions to collect money and unlock new abilities. Each run offers a unique combination of skills to take on a challenging boss. Defeat it to collect their essence and unlock powerful elemental ultimates.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>Game Features:</u></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Start Your Engines:</strong> Choose from a set of initial skills to gear up for the chaos of combat.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Battle the Basics:</strong> Survive relentless waves of geometric foes until the boss emerges.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Collect to Conquer:</strong> Amass experience and gold to enhance your Sphere's capabilities.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Power Up and Press On:</strong> Use your stash of gold to unlock transformative abilities and return stronger.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ultimate Geometric Showdown:</strong> Defeat all five Platonic Solids to claim your place in the heavens of shapes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3430380/extras/03c8b27602bf208ec16466f8cf6acd89.poster.avif?t=1751604163\" width=618 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3430380/extras/03c8b27602bf208ec16466f8cf6acd89.webm?t=1751604163\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3430380/extras/03c8b27602bf208ec16466f8cf6acd89.mp4?t=1751604163\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Rise of the Sphere</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Start in the realm of basic shapes, armed only with your wits and initial skills. Shoot, dodge, and weave through waves of lesser forms in a merciless battle against time and geometry.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3430380/extras/4a1f0f51efa03849fd6c8365d052ca75.avif?t=1751604163\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3430380/extras_big/4a1f0f51efa03849fd6c8365d052ca75.avif?t=1751604163 width=800 height=158 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3430380/extras/2c5bff831d1ff8219b1060247769933f.avif?t=1751604163\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3430380/extras_big/2c5bff831d1ff8219b1060247769933f.avif?t=1751604163 width=800 height=158 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3430380/extras/05b970bed6efa3a892db46c58b51dbb2.avif?t=1751604163\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3430380/extras_big/05b970bed6efa3a892db46c58b51dbb2.avif?t=1751604163 width=800 height=158 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Loot, Level, and Dominate</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Collect experience and gold from fallen adversaries, leveling up your Sphere's stats and strengthening your skills. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3430380/extras/5b1aad55e252509c9de1241f28be5b39.avif?t=1751604163\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3430380/extras_big/5b1aad55e252509c9de1241f28be5b39.avif?t=1751604163 width=800 height=428 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Rinse and Repeat with Rewards</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Didn't make it? No problem. Use the gold stashed from previous runs to beef up your Sphere with stronger stats and unlock new skills through game-changing Power Ups. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3430380/extras/7fb82d4983f9e0892e77e758bd34b769.avif?t=1751604163\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3430380/extras_big/7fb82d4983f9e0892e77e758bd34b769.avif?t=1751604163 width=800 height=802 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Summon and Conquer</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prove your worth by defeating enough lesser forms to summon the dreaded Platonic Bosses. Each boss battle is a test of endurance, skill, and your ability to think outside the cube.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3430380/extras/cad6783e2fdbf01351f9e3d51684ae62.avif?t=1751604163\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3430380/extras_big/cad6783e2fdbf01351f9e3d51684ae62.avif?t=1751604163 width=800 height=430 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Face the Final Five</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each run brings you closer to the ultimate challenge: defeating each of the five Platonic Solids, earning their essence and unlocking the ultimate elemental skills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3430380/extras/07d171152767cde1cc03964f0b39381d.avif?t=1751604163\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3430380/extras_big/07d171152767cde1cc03964f0b39381d.avif?t=1751604163 width=800 height=410 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ready your reflexes, sharpen your strategy, and may the best solid win!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prepare for a chaotic top-down, fast-paced shootout where you, as the Sphere, will fight the straight lines and rigid angles. Start with basic skills and grind your way through hordes of minions to collect money and unlock new abilities. Each run offers a unique combination of skills to take on a challenging boss. Defeat it to collect their essence and unlock powerful elemental ultimates.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>Game Features:</u></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Start Your Engines:</strong> Choose from a set of initial skills to gear up for the chaos of combat.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Battle the Basics:</strong> Survive relentless waves of geometric foes until the boss emerges.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Collect to Conquer:</strong> Amass experience and gold to enhance your Sphere's capabilities.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Power Up and Press On:</strong> Use your stash of gold to unlock transformative abilities and return stronger.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ultimate Geometric Showdown:</strong> Defeat all five Platonic Solids to claim your place in the heavens of shapes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3430380/extras/03c8b27602bf208ec16466f8cf6acd89.poster.avif?t=1751604163\" width=618 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3430380/extras/03c8b27602bf208ec16466f8cf6acd89.webm?t=1751604163\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3430380/extras/03c8b27602bf208ec16466f8cf6acd89.mp4?t=1751604163\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"