ass=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3430380/extras/07d171152767cde1cc03964f0b39381d.avif?t=1751604163\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3430380/extras_big/07d171152767cde1cc03964f0b39381d.avif?t=1751604163 width=800 height=410 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ready your reflexes, sharpen your strategy, and may the best solid win!</p>",
